Package ohos.data.search.schema

Class NoticeItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
      • ohos.data.search.schema.Schema<NoticeItem>
        • ohos.data.search.schema.NoticeItem

  • public final class NoticeItem
extends Schema<NoticeItem>
    Represents the index schema for notice items.

    This schema is used to create indexes for notice items. It supports index fields noticeDate, location, content, importance, latitude, longitude, repeatStatus, noticeCategory, and all the fields in CommonItem. Among these fields, identifier is mandatory and can be set via the CommonItem#setIdentifier(String) method.

    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
